The paper deals with a security problem in a wiretap network, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography (cs.CR). The network involves communication between nodes, which falls under the category of networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also discusses coding schemes and linear codes, which are topics in computer science (cs.CC) and signal processing (cs.SI).
